00:52:02,682 --> 00:52:05,083
that are in the mode that maybe aren't as discoverable.

1160
00:52:05,623 --> 00:52:06,843
Did you think about any other ways

1161
00:52:06,923 --> 00:52:08,204
to make them more discoverable?

