00:52:24,268 --> 00:52:28,169
But for various reasons, time being a primary one,

1170
00:52:28,749 --> 00:52:30,029
a lot of those things didn't happen.

1171
00:52:30,210 --> 00:52:31,590
And so in the course of production,

1172
00:52:31,710 --> 00:52:33,850
you kind of have to choose where your battles are

1173
00:52:33,910 --> 00:52:35,291
and you've got five bucks to spend.

