1189
00:53:13,829 --> 00:53:18,771
Early on, we had designers and artists primarily in the mix.

1190
00:53:18,791 --> 00:53:21,512
We also had an engineer and producers, of course.

1191
00:53:22,792 --> 00:53:26,654
And the early design direction of the big pitch,

1192
00:53:26,794 --> 00:53:28,914
firefight meets super puzzle fighter,

1193
00:53:29,515 --> 00:53:32,315
that was kind of from the directors of Forsaken

1194
00:53:32,536 --> 00:53:34,276
and from our creative lead, Lars.

1195
00:53:36,459 --> 00:53:38,760
