00:55:14,112 --> 00:55:18,254
Gambit Prime, we looked at how are we going to evolve Gambit?

1228
00:55:18,274 --> 00:55:20,075
What do we want to change about Gambit?

1229
00:55:20,275 --> 00:55:21,096
And there were a couple of things.

1230
00:55:21,156 --> 00:55:23,117
We often got people asking, hey, it'd be great

1231
00:55:23,157 --> 00:55:25,758
if as an invader I had something else that I could do, right?

1232
00:55:26,259 --> 00:55:28,680
And so that's kind of where the moat draining came from,

1233
00:55:29,020 --> 00:55:29,401
in part.

1234
00:55:30,621 --> 00:55:35,424
And then the roles of Gambit evolved somewhat organically.

1235
00:55:36,165 --> 00:55:37,585
And we looked at that and realized

1236
00:55:37,605 --> 00:55:39,066
that we had something really great.

1237
00:55:39,146 --> 00:55:41,147
One of the success factors of Gambit was that

1238
00:55:41,928 --> 00:55:43,769
I could be the collector while you're the killer

1239
00:55:43,869 --> 00:55:45,810
and you're doing this other, you're the invader

1240
00:55:45,890 --> 00:55:47,411
and we could each have a role in the game.

1241
00:55:47,452 --> 00:55:50,413
And so we thought that is part of what makes Gambit special.

1242
00:55:50,854 --> 00:55:52,215
Let's really double down there.

