1268
00:57:12,086 --> 00:57:15,028
And there are other people on the team who are looking at,

1269
00:57:15,128 --> 00:57:19,290
hey, how are we going to keep players occupied throughout the Destiny ecosystem?

1270
00:57:19,331 --> 00:57:21,332
