1320
00:59:29,903 --> 00:59:30,343
still need more.

1321
00:59:30,923 --> 00:59:31,464
Still need more.

1322
00:59:31,724 --> 00:59:33,485
And we kind of built it as we went.

1323
00:59:34,046 --> 00:59:34,326
Thank you.

1324
00:59:34,686 --> 00:59:34,846
Sure.

