01:00:07,436 --> 01:00:09,296
And we're always looking at it.

1334
01:00:10,297 --> 01:00:11,677
Think about Bungie, and this is one of the things

1335
01:00:11,697 --> 01:00:13,658
that impressed me when I was first joining the company,

1336
01:00:14,219 --> 01:00:16,199
