01:02:22,450 --> 01:02:25,273
So I think the first part of your question was,

1393
01:02:25,333 --> 01:02:26,113
how big was the team?

1394
01:02:26,293 --> 01:02:28,996
So initially there were, I think,

1395
01:02:29,096 --> 01:02:31,839
four or five of us on the team for the first couple of months.

1396
01:02:32,559 --> 01:02:36,443
And that grew as more people became available

1397
01:02:36,543 --> 01:02:37,925
and we could bring the resources on,

1398
01:02:37,985 --> 01:02:40,987
but also as we knew more about what we were making.

1399
01:02:41,488 --> 01:02:48,132
