01:03:12,076 --> 01:03:13,077
the second part of your question.

1405
01:03:13,657 --> 01:03:14,777
About the name of the game.

1406
01:03:14,857 --> 01:03:15,717
Why is it called Gambit?

1407
01:03:15,757 --> 01:03:16,957
Oh, why is it called Gambit?

1408
01:03:17,237 --> 01:03:18,658
You know, that was originally just the code name.

1409
01:03:18,758 --> 01:03:20,958
It was code name Gambit before we even knew what it was.

1410
01:03:21,178 --> 01:03:24,059
It was like, okay, it's Firefight meets Puzzle Fighter,

1411
01:03:24,439 --> 01:03:25,539
and it's code name Gambit.

1412
01:03:25,619 --> 01:03:28,719
And then, as so often happens in development,

1413
01:03:28,760 --> 01:03:31,700
