1414
01:03:31,820 --> 01:03:32,300
And it stuck.

1415
01:03:33,020 --> 01:03:34,181
So we had it from the very beginning.

1416
01:03:34,201 --> 01:03:35,661
There was no marketing invention.

1417
01:03:35,821 --> 01:03:36,781
No, it was actually, yeah.

1418
01:03:38,601 --> 01:03:39,582
Day one, it was Gambit.

