1424
01:04:01,576 --> 01:04:04,558
Okay, the second question I had was on Gambit Prime,

1425
01:04:06,219 --> 01:04:07,520
was it ever considered the,

1426
01:04:07,860 --> 01:04:10,002
instead of farming for three different armor tiers

1427
01:04:10,322 --> 01:04:14,064
in Reckoning, having the tiers unlock as you,

1428
01:04:14,525 --> 01:04:17,126
or a single piece of armor that would unlock

1429
01:04:17,186 --> 01:04:19,528
the additional tiers as you completed those tiers?

