1440
01:05:11,216 --> 01:05:13,097
that once Tier 3 becomes available,

1441
01:05:13,417 --> 01:05:15,017
people are going to be focused on Tier 3,

1442
01:05:15,137 --> 01:05:15,998
and we're okay with that.

