01:08:01,766 --> 01:08:03,987
whereas most designers do not have the permissions

1510
01:08:04,027 --> 01:08:05,368
to check code in, that kind of thing.

1511
01:08:06,088 --> 01:08:06,848
Cool, thank you.

1512
01:08:08,829 --> 01:08:09,370
A few things.

1513
01:08:09,710 --> 01:08:12,411
First, can we get your voiceovers in Gamut

1514
01:08:12,591 --> 01:08:13,531
as a DLC, please?

1515
01:08:13,551 --> 01:08:14,672
Because that would be amazing.

1516
01:08:14,792 --> 01:08:16,373
The team has asked about that, too.

1517
01:08:17,561 --> 01:08:22,671
Yeah, though thankfully I don't have a SAG card, so we couldn't actually ship my voice.

1518
01:08:22,911 --> 01:08:30,145
Okay, other thing, did you anticipate linear fusion rifles being so dominant in Gambit when you invade?

1519
01:08:31,135 --> 01:08:33,715
We did not.

1520
01:08:33,875 --> 01:08:37,076
We really expected that supers would be a lot more prevalent.

1521
01:08:37,916 --> 01:08:40,197
And especially roaming supers, we thought were going to be.

1522
01:08:40,577 --> 01:08:44,477
I think the bet was that Golden Gun was going

1523
01:08:44,497 --> 01:08:46,098
to be the thing to beat in Gambit.

1524
01:08:47,278 --> 01:08:48,758
And we knew about snipers.

1525
01:08:48,778 --> 01:08:50,279
We were certainly using a bunch of those.

1526
01:08:50,359 --> 01:08:54,059
But the rise of linear fusion rifles in the Gambit meta

1527
01:08:54,099 --> 01:08:55,780
was definitely not expected.

1528
01:08:55,800 --> 01:08:57,500
And part of that is because.

1529
01:08:58,695 --> 01:09:00,477
After one day of being out in the wild,

1530
01:09:00,677 --> 01:09:03,479
the game received way more playtesting,

1531
01:09:03,499 --> 01:09:05,742
like a gazillion times more playtesting

1532
01:09:05,782 --> 01:09:07,844
than it had received internally up until that point

1533
01:09:07,904 --> 01:09:09,545
because just math, right?

1534
01:09:09,785 --> 01:09:11,467
There's a limited number of people at Bungie

1535
01:09:11,607 --> 01:09:14,270
and there's like way more players out in the world.

1536
01:09:14,650 --> 01:09:18,874
And so the meta evolved in a way that our small group didn't anticipate.

1537
01:09:18,934 --> 01:09:22,697
And that's just one of those things that you have to be prepared for and react to.

1538
01:09:22,777 --> 01:09:28,082
And so we tuned linear fusion rifles to kind of bring down their efficacy in

1539
01:09:28,102 --> 01:09:29,303
Gambit as a result of that.

1540
01:09:30,864 --> 01:09:35,628
And we're also aware of, for future map development,

1541
01:09:35,849 --> 01:09:38,111
maybe that will impact how we design maps so

1542
01:09:38,151 --> 01:09:41,794
that linear fusion rifles may not have as much of an impact in the future.

1543
01:09:42,154 --> 01:09:44,658
But, maybe. Or we might decide that we're going to lean into it.

1544
01:09:45,018 --> 01:09:46,340
We never know what we decide to do.

1545
01:09:47,181 --> 01:09:47,782
Awesome. Thank you.

